```vim
:h buffers
:ls
:bd
:b 3
:h new-vim-server
```

```terminal
vim --servername VIM-SERVER route.rb
vim --servername VIM-SERVER --remote-silent route.rb
```

```.vimrc
set laststatus=2
set statusline=%F:\ %l
set hidden "in order to switch between buffers with unsaved change
map <s-tab> :bp<cr>
map <tab> :bn<cr>
```
